    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2226660/extras/eb65681d773948908263f6f80a7aaa38.poster.avif?t=1687724079\" width=600 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2226660/extras/eb65681d773948908263f6f80a7aaa38.webm?t=1687724079\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><strong>Yamorn曾经是一个繁荣兴旺的城镇，但现在却被瘟疫所葬送。</strong><br>作为Yamorn卫队的队长，你必须竭尽所能拯救尽可能多的无辜生命，即使这意味着清除那些已经受到这种病痛侵袭的人，并引领他们走出这个被上帝遗弃的地狱。<br>作为一名瘟疫医生，在收到一封神秘信函后，你前往Yamorn，唯一的目标和职责是清除所有感染者，揭开这种感染的秘密，并根除它的根源。<br>探索废墟镇及其周边地区，在废墟中搜寻材料，寻找并制作新的攻击和防御物品。<br>从投机取巧的盗墓贼那里购买拾得的东西。<br>利用瘟疫赋予的力量，获得能力并在战斗中增加胜算。<br><i>没有其他人会来帮助你。</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2226660/extras/8c410666b5578c0cc7fe720047e5439b.poster.avif?t=1687724079\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2226660/extras/8c410666b5578c0cc7fe720047e5439b.webm?t=1687724079\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2226660/extras/8c410666b5578c0cc7fe720047e5439b.mp4?t=1687724079\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
